<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- قَائِمًا.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- يَحُثُّهُمْ فِي الفِطْرِ عَلَى الصَّدَقَةِ، وَيُبيِّنُ لَهُمْ مَا يُخْرِجُونَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- وَيُرَغِّبُهُمْ فِي الأَضْحَى فِي الأُضْحِيَّةِ، وَيُبَيِّنُ لَهُمْ حُكْمَهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- التَّكْبِيرَاتُ الزَّوَائِدُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- وَالذِّكْرُ بَيْنَهَا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَالخُطْبَتَانِ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>سُنَّةٌ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَكُرِهَ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- تَنَفُّلٌ، وَقَضَاءُ فَائِتَةٍ قَبْلَ الصَّلَاةِ بِمَوْضِعِهَا.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- وَبَعْدَهَا قَبْلَ مُفَارَقَتِهِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَسُنَّ لِمَنْ فَاتَتْهُ:</span> قَضَاؤُهَا فِي يَوْمِهَا عَلَى صِفَتِهَا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>- وَسُنَّ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>- التَّكْبِيرُ المُطْلَقُ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>